s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:22114:\"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Without a doubt, the SEO plugin is one of the essential WordPress plugins ever. When selecting the finest WordPress SEO plugin, most people choose well-known plugins without giving much thought to alternatives. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">What if you could have gotten a lot more done with a WordPress SEO plugin that&#8217;s a lot better and comes with a lot more features for free? Yes, we’re discussing </span><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/seo-by-rank-math/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rank Math</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> in this article. It&#8217;s not a Rank Math review; instead, it&#8217;s about why Rank Math is the best SEO plugin in the market.</span></p>\n<h2>1. Easy Setup Wizard</h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">When you first start Rank Math, a setup wizard appears to assist you in configuring the essential functions. To activate various features, you can also link your free Rank Math account. You don&#8217;t have to link to a free account to use the plugin, but you will need it to unlock all features. </span></p>\n<blockquote><p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">“One of the reasons why we love the Rank Math SEO plugin and use it on our clients’ website is because of its ease of setup and use. It’s really intuitive,” says Donald Chan, founder of </span><a href=\"https://www.impactbc.com.sg/services/web-design/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Singapore-based web design agency IMPACT</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. </span></p></blockquote>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Overall, the wizard is well-designed and provides tailored experiences for novice and advanced users. When you </span><a href=\"https://rankmath.com/kb/installing-through-the-admin-panel/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">install and activate the Rank Math plugin</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, it will instantly launch the setup wizard, allowing you to adjust all basic SEO settings straight away.</span></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-23339\" src=\"http://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Easy-Setup-Wizard.png\" alt=\"Easy Setup Wizard\" width=\"1051\" height=\"1069\" srcset=\"https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Easy-Setup-Wizard.png 1051w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Easy-Setup-Wizard-295x300.png 295w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Easy-Setup-Wizard-1007x1024.png 1007w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Easy-Setup-Wizard-768x781.png 768w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Easy-Setup-Wizard-570x580.png 570w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1051px) 100vw, 1051px\" /></p>\n<p><span class=\"c2\">You can launch the setup wizard by navigating to </span><span class=\"c6 c2\">Rank Math &gt; Dashboard</span><span class=\"c2\"> and clicking on the </span><span class=\"c6 c2\">Setup Wizard</span><span class=\"c6 c2\"> </span><span class=\"c2\">tab.</span></p>\n<h2 id=\"h.29onqbiyilm5\" class=\"c3\"><span class=\"c17 c6 c15\">2. Built-in Advanced SEO Analytics Module</span></h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rank Math’s advanced SEO analytics module provides you with valuable information regarding the keywords, sitemap status, and indexing issues that you come across. The Pro version of Rank Math incorporates data from the Google Search Console. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Red and green arrows indicate whether the metrics of a post have increased (or dropped) over time. Google Search Console lacks these handy arrows. Rank Math makes it simple to see whether your content is improving (or deteriorating) over time, and you can also keep an eye on your </span><a href=\"https://rankmath.com/kb/analytics/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">top 5 winning or losing posts</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">.</span></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-23340\" src=\"http://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/top-5-winning-keywords.jpg\" alt=\"top 5 winning or losing posts\" width=\"1999\" height=\"975\" srcset=\"https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/top-5-winning-keywords.jpg 1999w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/top-5-winning-keywords-300x146.jpg 300w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/top-5-winning-keywords-1024x499.jpg 1024w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/top-5-winning-keywords-768x375.jpg 768w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/top-5-winning-keywords-1536x749.jpg 1536w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/top-5-winning-keywords-570x278.jpg 570w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1999px) 100vw, 1999px\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Not only this, but Rank Math’s </span><a href=\"https://rankmath.com/kb/add-multiple-keywords-to-rank-tracker/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rank Tracker</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> feature allows you to keep a watch on your website’s keywords. To do so, navigate to </span><b>Rank Math &gt; Analytics &gt; Rank Tracker </b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">inside your WordPress dashboard as shown below:</span></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-23341\" src=\"http://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Rank-Tracker.jpg\" alt=\" Rank Tracker\" width=\"1999\" height=\"834\" srcset=\"https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Rank-Tracker.jpg 1999w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Rank-Tracker-300x125.jpg 300w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Rank-Tracker-1024x427.jpg 1024w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Rank-Tracker-768x320.jpg 768w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Rank-Tracker-1536x641.jpg 1536w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Rank-Tracker-570x238.jpg 570w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1999px) 100vw, 1999px\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Also, the Rank Math Analytics module can </span><a href=\"https://rankmath.com/kb/seo-email-reporting/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">deliver SEO reports in your inbox</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. The advanced analytics module of Rank Math itself offers so many features that’ll help you optimise your site with ease and ultimately help your site rank higher in the search engines.</span></p>\n<h2>3. Advanced Schema Generator</h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The advanced Schema Generator makes it easy for you to add Schema markup types to your posts. Rank Math’s </span><a href=\"https://rankmath.com/pricing/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">PRO version</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> also includes </span><a href=\"https://rankmath.com/kb/schema-generator/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Custom Schema Generator</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> that quickly adds custom Schema </span><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">to your posts.</span></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-23342\" src=\"http://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Advanced-Schema-Generator.png\" alt=\"Advanced Schema Generator\" width=\"1999\" height=\"936\" srcset=\"https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Advanced-Schema-Generator.png 1999w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Advanced-Schema-Generator-300x140.png 300w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Advanced-Schema-Generator-1024x479.png 1024w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Advanced-Schema-Generator-768x360.png 768w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Advanced-Schema-Generator-1536x719.png 1536w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Advanced-Schema-Generator-570x267.png 570w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1999px) 100vw, 1999px\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Not only this, but you can also save the custom Schema as a template to reuse it on some other posts or pages.</span></p>\n<h2>4. 20+ Predefined Schema Markup Types</h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You need to be familiar with schema markup if you wish to increase the SEO of your website. The Schema markup helps you to stand out in the search engine result pages.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rank Math supports 20+ predefined Schema types, and </span><a href=\"https://rankmath.com/kb/rich-snippets/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">adding structured data</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> to your posts with the help of Rank Math is extremely simple. You can add rich snippets based on the schema type you choose from a vast list of Schema types (Article, Video, Event, Recipe, Product, and much more).</span></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-23343\" src=\"http://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20-Predefined-Schema-Markup-Types.png\" alt=\"20+ Predefined Schema Markup Types\" width=\"990\" height=\"1999\" srcset=\"https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20-Predefined-Schema-Markup-Types.png 990w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20-Predefined-Schema-Markup-Types-149x300.png 149w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20-Predefined-Schema-Markup-Types-507x1024.png 507w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20-Predefined-Schema-Markup-Types-768x1551.png 768w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20-Predefined-Schema-Markup-Types-761x1536.png 761w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/20-Predefined-Schema-Markup-Types-570x1151.png 570w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 990px) 100vw, 990px\" /></p>\n<h2>5. Advanced Image SEO Module</h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rank Math automatically </span><a href=\"https://rankmath.com/kb/image-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">adds alt attributes to images</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">. It saves a lot of time as WordPress core has stopped adding alt text automatically. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rank Math, as always, turns out to be a game-changer, as it automatically adds alt and title attributes to your images. The Image SEO module of Rank Math thereby reduces your manual work and helps save your valuable time.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">To benefit from the Image SEO features provided by Rank Math, navigate to </span><b>Rank Math &gt; Dashboard &gt; Modules</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> in your WordPress dashboard and enable the </span><b>Image SEO</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> module as shown below.</span></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-23344\" src=\"http://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Advanced-Image-SEO-Module.jpg\" alt=\"Advanced Image SEO Module\" width=\"915\" height=\"352\" srcset=\"https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Advanced-Image-SEO-Module.jpg 915w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Advanced-Image-SEO-Module-300x115.jpg 300w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Advanced-Image-SEO-Module-768x295.jpg 768w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Advanced-Image-SEO-Module-570x219.jpg 570w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 915px) 100vw, 915px\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">You can then locate the image optimization settings from the Rank Math menu. To do so, navigate to </span><b>General Settings &gt; Images</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> as shown below:</span></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-23345\" src=\"http://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/add-missing-alt-attributes.jpg\" alt=\"add missing alt attributes\" width=\"1956\" height=\"1042\" srcset=\"https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/add-missing-alt-attributes.jpg 1956w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/add-missing-alt-attributes-300x160.jpg 300w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/add-missing-alt-attributes-1024x546.jpg 1024w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/add-missing-alt-attributes-768x409.jpg 768w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/add-missing-alt-attributes-1536x818.jpg 1536w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/add-missing-alt-attributes-570x304.jpg 570w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1956px) 100vw, 1956px\" /></p>\n<h2>6. Local SEO Optimization</h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Local SEO also aids in maintaining the accuracy of your Google My Business (GMB) profile so that it is trustworthy, appealing, and has a better chance of appearing in the local pack. You&#8217;ll be able to attract and engage a larger audience with an up-to-date Google My Business profile, resulting in increased website traffic.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Through Rank Math’s </span><a href=\"https://rankmath.com/kb/local-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">local SEO support</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, your site can receive even more traffic. You need to enter your business information in Rank Math, and the necessary metadata will be added to your website, thereby increasing its ranking potential.</span></p>\n<h2>7. Bulk Edit Options</h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With Rank Math’s </span><a href=\"https://rankmath.com/kb/bulk-editing-in-rank-math/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">bulk edit options</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, you can bulk select posts to noindex, index, nofollow, delete custom canonical URLs, redirect them all, and much more. You need not waste time travelling back and forth between editing windows for every post or page on your site.</span></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-23346\" src=\"http://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Bulk-Edit-Options.jpg\" alt=\"Bulk Edit Options\" width=\"1999\" height=\"1073\" srcset=\"https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Bulk-Edit-Options.jpg 1999w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Bulk-Edit-Options-300x161.jpg 300w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Bulk-Edit-Options-1024x550.jpg 1024w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Bulk-Edit-Options-768x412.jpg 768w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Bulk-Edit-Options-1536x824.jpg 1536w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Bulk-Edit-Options-570x306.jpg 570w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1999px) 100vw, 1999px\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Not only this, but Rank Math’s quick edit options allow you to easily edit your SEO metadata directly from your WordPress posts or pages area as shown :</span></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-23347\" src=\"http://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/SEO-metadata.jpg\" alt=\"SEO metadata\" width=\"1999\" height=\"945\" srcset=\"https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/SEO-metadata.jpg 1999w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/SEO-metadata-300x142.jpg 300w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/SEO-metadata-1024x484.jpg 1024w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/SEO-metadata-768x363.jpg 768w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/SEO-metadata-1536x726.jpg 1536w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/SEO-metadata-570x269.jpg 570w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1999px) 100vw, 1999px\" /></p>\n<h2>8. WooCommerce SEO</h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rank Math’s </span><a href=\"https://rankmath.com/blog/woocommerce-seo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">WooCommerce SEO</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> helps you optimise your product pages and boost sales. WooCommerce&#8217;s user-friendly and appealing features make it simple for your website to rank higher in search engines.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">WooCommerce SEO is available within its free version. Rank Math’s PRO version offers </span><a href=\"https://rankmath.com/kb/woocommerce-seo-feature-comparison/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">additional features</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> delivering everything you&#8217;ll need for your WooCommerce SEO. </span></p>\n<h2>9. Focus Keyword and Content Analysis</h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">By default, Rank Math allows you to assign </span><a href=\"https://rankmath.com/kb/keyword-research-with-rank-math/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">five keywords</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> to your posts, whereas, in the PRO version, you can add an unlimited number of target keywords.</span></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-23349\" src=\"http://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Focus-Keyword-and-Content-Analysis.jpg\" alt=\"Focus Keyword and Content Analysis\" width=\"642\" height=\"642\" srcset=\"https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Focus-Keyword-and-Content-Analysis.jpg 642w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Focus-Keyword-and-Content-Analysis-300x300.jpg 300w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Focus-Keyword-and-Content-Analysis-150x150.jpg 150w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Focus-Keyword-and-Content-Analysis-100x100.jpg 100w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Focus-Keyword-and-Content-Analysis-570x570.jpg 570w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 642px) 100vw, 642px\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rank Math demands you to include your keyword in the first paragraph rather than the first sentence, indicating that it adheres to current benchmarks. Rank Math provides keyword ideas when you type a keyword into the &#8220;focus keyword&#8221; textbox. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">It will give you a color-coded score between 0 and 100 points. Rank Math will provide recommendations to help you improve your content even more. For example, you&#8217;ll get suggestions for integrating your focus keyword in your text and title for SEO purposes.</span></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-23350\" src=\"http://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/color-coded-score-on-rank-math.jpg\" alt=\"color-coded score on rank math\" width=\"986\" height=\"531\" srcset=\"https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/color-coded-score-on-rank-math.jpg 986w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/color-coded-score-on-rank-math-300x162.jpg 300w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/color-coded-score-on-rank-math-768x414.jpg 768w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/color-coded-score-on-rank-math-570x307.jpg 570w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 986px) 100vw, 986px\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rank Math’s PRO version also has a </span><a href=\"https://rankmath.com/kb/score-100-in-tests/#google-trends-for-focus-keywords\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Google Trends</span></a><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> feature to bring up a graph and showcase more relevant data on your selected keywords.</span></p>\n<h2>10. SEO Overview Of Website’s Content</h2>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With the help of Rank Math, you can monitor the outcomes of your SEO efforts on a single screen and always know where you stand in terms of SEO. It gives you a bird&#8217;s eye perspective of your posts&#8217; overall optimisation. It displays your website&#8217;s overall optimisation score and the number of posts with good, fair, or poor optimisation.</span></p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-23351\" src=\"http://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/SEO-Overview-Of-Websites-Content.jpg\" alt=\"SEO Overview Of Website’s Content\" width=\"1999\" height=\"1127\" srcset=\"https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/SEO-Overview-Of-Websites-Content.jpg 1999w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/SEO-Overview-Of-Websites-Content-300x169.jpg 300w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/SEO-Overview-Of-Websites-Content-1024x577.jpg 1024w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/SEO-Overview-Of-Websites-Content-768x433.jpg 768w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/SEO-Overview-Of-Websites-Content-1536x866.jpg 1536w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/SEO-Overview-Of-Websites-Content-128x72.jpg 128w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/SEO-Overview-Of-Websites-Content-570x321.jpg 570w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1999px) 100vw, 1999px\" /></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Rank Math is causing quite a stir in the market as it has the most advanced functionality most of it free of charge. </span></p>\n<p><b>Conclusion</b></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The plugin&#8217;s Pro and Business editions are quite inventive, with fantastic additional capabilities like Google Search Console and Google Analytics data integration. It might be a game-changer to have this SEO performance statistics right in your WordPress dashboard. After all, if you don&#8217;t measure it, you won&#8217;t be able to improve it. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you aren’t  Rank Math on your site, it’s time for you to rollup your sleeves and install Rank Math now! This plugin is extremely helpful to WordPress users with advanced SEO knowledge and skills. What do you think about Rank Math? Let us know in the comments section. We are happy to hear from you.</span></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://jeweltheme.com/rank-math-is-the-best-seo-plugin/\">Rank Math is the Best SEO Plugin, and Here are 10 Reasons Why</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://jeweltheme.com\">Jewel Theme</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:61:\"https://jeweltheme.com/rank-math-is-the-best-seo-plugin/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:30:\"com-wordpress:feed-additions:1\";a:1:{s:7:\"post-id\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:5:\"23337\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:73:\"\n		\n		\n					\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n\n					\n										\n					\n					\n			\n		\n		\n			\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:63:\"Best Elements For Blogger &amp; Marketer To Create Awesome Page\";s:7: