ite. Plus, Gentelella includes many more website elements, tabs, layouts, level menus, charts, and forms, etc.</p>\n<h2><a href=\"https://github.com/puikinsh/nalika\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Nalika</a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/puikinsh/nalika\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-23257 size-full\" src=\"http://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Nalika.jpg\" alt=\"Nalika Admin Template \" width=\"850\" height=\"476\" srcset=\"https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Nalika.jpg 850w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Nalika-300x168.jpg 300w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Nalika-768x430.jpg 768w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Nalika-128x72.jpg 128w, https://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Nalika-570x319.jpg 570w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px\" /></a></p>\n<p>If you’re searching for a free dark mode admin dashboard, Nalika would be a good choice for you.</p>\n<p>Nowadays, most of the devices support dark mode including Mac and Windows. That is why all software developers try to set up dark mode. You can easily and watch the contents on your device. Therefore, if you use Nalika dark mode admin template, then your online stores will look darker but smarter. In this way, it will be helpful for your user&#8217;s eye. Reducing eyestrain it lets the user browse your site at ease.</p>\n<p>Plus, the Nalika dashboard template incorporates almost the same design as the aforementioned Jeweler dashboard. Both of the templates are from one creator. Yet, Nalika is supportive of users. On the other hand, Jeweler is for the website admin.</p>\n<p>That is to say, Nalika is a perfect template for those who want to build up a community for online shoppers most likely the Amazon Spark. Your user can maintain a user account with the<br />\nNalika template. Moreover, there are some pre-built popular social m