s Plugin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"http://jeweltheme.com/?p=22885\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:215:\"<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://jeweltheme.com/best-elementor-addons/\">15+ must have best Free Elementor Addons</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://jeweltheme.com\">Jewel Theme</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:12:\"Liton Arefin\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30875:\"<style type=\"text/css\"></style>\n<section class=\"kc-elm kc-css-3306302 kc_row\">\n<div class=\"kc-row-container  kc-container\">\n<div class=\"kc-wrap-columns\">\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1455073 kc_col-sm-12 kc_column kc_col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"kc-col-container\">\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1485831 kc_text_block\">\n<p>If you are in a search for getting extra functionalities to the Elementor, then you are just in the right place. In this article, I&#8217;m going to take you through some best of the best Elementor Addons. <span id=\"more-22885\"></span></p>\n<p>Nowadays WordPress is so powerful with its flexibility, easy customizable method, and with many useful features. However, it is getting more powerful because of the Elementor plugin. Elementor is a page builder plugin. You can use elementor addons to make the website more powerful. Both the pro and free Elementors will obviously supercharge your website buildings experience. Free always has its limitations that&#8217;s why you can go with some <a href=\"https://www.wppagebuilders.com/premium-elementor-addons/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">premium Elementor Addons</a>.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1454261 kc_text_block\">\n<p>Most of the addons in our guide will give you a variety of new Elementor widgets to customize your designs. Besides, some Elementors can also add new functionalities or new design options as well.<br />By using elementor and its best and free addons, you will be able to make any type of website. Likewise, blogging, e-commerce, business or even portfolio websites. In case if you don&#8217;t get the proper one from this article you can check some other <a href=\"https://dessign.net/free-elementor-plugins/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Free Elementor Addons</a> too.</p>\n<p>Today, here in this blog post you will get a sharp look-out on best elementor addons. Know which are the Best elementor addons for WordPress in 2022. So, check out the best Elementor Addons given below and pick your favorite one! </p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-3640308 kc_text_block\">\n<h2>1.<a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/master-addons/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Master Addons for Elementor</a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/master-addons/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/Master-Addons-for-Elementor.jpg\" alt=\"Master Addons for Elementor\" width=\"772\" height=\"250\" /></a></p>\n<p>Master Addons for Elementor is the classiest addons for the Elementor WordPress site. If you want to create a new WordPress website using elementor, you will have to use additional add-ons to add more flexibility. Besides, the plugin includes accurately developed Elementor blocks.</p>\n<p>It comes with more than 30 free elements. All the same, every element incorporates tons of features. And what you want even more, you have option of a premium version with more blocks as well.</p>\n<p>The premium version comes with the Master Addons animated headlines, image galleries, news ticker and blog. Thus, you can build your own trendy news or magazine style site. For more, this plugin also has blocks for dual headings, tabs, info box, changelog, call to action creative buttons, table of contents, and pricing tables and many more.</p>\n<p>Moreover, many user-friendly and free templates are available with this plugin. What&#039;s more, using Master Addons, you will get free support and updates. And as a bonus, you can use 11 themes to adjust or design your site!</p>\n<p>Features you mustn&#039;t miss:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>30+ free but powerful elements.</li>\n<li>50+ ready-made block to import easily.</li>\n<li>5+ Different modules of header and footer blocks.</li>\n<li>Lightweight and fast.</li>\n<li>Free templates available.</li>\n<li>Premium version available with extensive features.</li>\n<li>Easy to import and export feature.</li>\n<li>Simplest and easy to use.</li>\n<li>Fast and responsive layout.</li>\n<li>Developed by trusted developer.</li>\n<li>Lifetime support and free updates.</li>\n<li>24/7 dedicated support.</li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-340545 kc_text_block\">\n<h2>2. <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/content-locker-for-elementor/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Content Locker for Elementor</a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/plugins/content-locker-for-elementor/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/05/content-locker-for-elementor.jpg\" alt=\"Content Locker For Elementor\" width=\"772\" height=\"250\" /></a></p>\n<p>Content Locker for Elementor is a Plugin that helps you to restrict harmful access to your content. It works in different strategies for content rest