ers you millions of theme in its directories. But here the question occurs which one to choose? Well, the long list of the heme might confuse you. So today in this article I am going to describe to you about one of the most popular theme, OceanWP. OceanWP is one of the powerful theme built up with multiple amazing features. With its features and popularity, OceanWP is able to get more than 400K active installation. Isn’t it wow?</p>\n<p>So I suggest you choose this theme once and believe me you will get an impressive result for your site. Whether you are a developer or a layman, you can easily tackle the theme OceanWP. It is user-friendly and very easy to deal with. It gives you easy access to customize your website in a beautiful way. Now before diving into the theme let me introduce you with its key features.</p>\n</div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1905021 kc_text_block\">\n<p><strong>Key Features</strong></p>\n<ol>\n<li>Cost: Free</li>\n<li>Type: WordPress Theme</li>\n<li>Active Installation: 400000+</li>\n<li>Rating: 5 out of 5</li>\n</ol>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-3704406 kc_row kc_row_inner\">\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-3745691 kc_col-of-5 kc_column_inner kc_col-of-5\">\n<div class=\"kc_wrapper kc-col-inner-container\"></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-2016570 kc_col-of-5 kc_column_inner kc_col-of-5\">\n<div class=\"kc_wrapper kc-col-inner-container\">\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-376141\">\n	<a class=\"kc_button\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/oceanwp/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"oceanwp\" onclick=\"\"><br />\n		Download	</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1135014 kc_col-of-5 kc_column_inner kc_col-of-5\">\n<div class=\"kc_wrapper kc-col-inner-container\">\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1878686\">\n	<a class=\"kc_button\" href=\"https://oceanwp.org/demos/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"oceanwp\" onclick=\"\"><br />\n		Demo	</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-2338752 kc_col-of-5 kc_column_inner kc_col-of-5\">\n<div class=\"kc_wrapper kc-col-inner-container\">\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-3819654\">\n	<a class=\"kc_button\" href=\"https://docs.oceanwp.org/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"oceanwp\" onclick=\"\"><br />\n		Documentation	</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-3217810 kc_col-of-5 kc_column_inner kc_col-of-5\">\n<div class=\"kc_wrapper kc-col-inner-container\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1766755 kc_row kc_row_inner\">\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-723807 kc_col-sm-12 kc_column_inner kc_col-sm-12\">\n<div class=\"kc_wrapper kc-col-inner-container\">\n<div class=\"kc-elm kc-css-1854640 kc_text_block\">\n<h2>The reason for getting 400+K Active Install of free WordPress theme OceanWP</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Easy to implement</li>\n<li>No coding knowledge is required</li>\n<li>Awesome free and premium available demos</li>\n<li>Responsive side panel with respective widgets</li>\n<li>Social sharing option</li>\n<li>Built-in SEO</li>\n<li>Compatible with PHP 7.1</li>\n<li>Runs with the fastest speed</li>\n<li>Translation ready</li>\n<li>Compatible with WPML plugin</li>\n<li>E-commerce ready</li>\n</ul>\n<p>To get more information about the theme, let us elaborate some of its features in detail. So let’s get started:</p>\n<h2>Single Click Demo Content</h2>\n<p>OceanWP, an ideal WordPress theme offers you several demos which all are stunning and stylish. Its demos are easy to implement which can be done with your single click. Within a couple of seconds, your website is ready just like a demo. You just have to customize the data of your website as per requirement. For additional change or if you want more or something different than the available demos, you can create it with your own. Some of the demos are blogger demo, travel demo and coach demo.</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/OcenWP-demos.png\" alt=\"OcenWP demos\" width=\"1634\" height=\"686\" /></p>\n<p>OceanWP is not limited to it, as it offers some more additional demos which are listed below:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Simple</li>\n<li>Stylish</li>\n<li>Architect</li>\n<li>Gym Club</li>\n<li>Lawyer</li>\n<li>Store</li>\n<li>Personal</li>\n<li>Yoga</li>\n<li>Mega Gym</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>WooCommerce Ready</h2>\n<p>Another reason for the popularity of any site is it should be WooCommerce ready. If you are about to create your website for commercial purpose then, OceanWP is the best option for you. It will arrange all the content of your site in the right place. The theme is compatible with the latest version of WooCommerce so you will not face any issues regarding plugin incompatibility.</p>\n<p>Hence you will get great customization for your website with which you will able to maintain top rank at the search engine.</p>\n<h2>Detail Documentation</h2>\n<p>A proper guideline can make any work easier for you, isn’t it? So here documentation is like your guideline which will help to deal with this theme. With this, even beginners can use this theme and able to create a wonderful website. OceanWP offers you documentation for both free and premium version which is available in both video and written format. So not to worry anymore, get your website ready with this amazing theme, OceanWP.</p>\n<h2>Fully Responsive</h2>\n<p>Nowadays many people are using mobile or tablet for visiting any site. You must create your site in such a way that, it should be responsive for all sizes of screen. If your site is limited, it will be worthless. So in such case, you can use OceanWP which is developed with responsive design. If you are using this theme, your websites can easily detect any size of the visitor’s screen. The page layout will automatically change according to the screen from which visitor is visiting your site. It is another awesome feature of this WordPress theme which makes your website different from others and gives an elegant appearance. </p>\n<h2>Outstanding Theme Panel and Customizer</h2>\n<p>OceanWP offers you an amazing theme panel. It will help you to enable and disable all sorts of things. It gives you easy access to customize your website. Some of the shortcuts of the theme panel are:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Upload your logo</li>\n<li>Add your favicon</li>\n<li>Choose your primary color</li>\n<li>Choose your typography</li>\n<li>Top bar options</li>\n<li>Header options</li>\n<li>Footer widget options</li>\n<li>Footer bottom options</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Besides these, all OceanWP has several more features. Some of them are listed below:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Easy to setup</li>\n<li>A dedicated and high priority of support</li>\n<li>Well detailed documentation</li>\n<li>Free templates</li>\n<li>Fully customizable</li>\n<li>RTL Support</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Extension of OceanWP</h2>\n<p>OceanWP comes with 8 free and 13 premium extension which is listed below:</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full\" src=\"http://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/OcenWP-extensions.png\" alt=\"OcenWP extensions\" width=\"1587\" height=\"869\" /></p>\n<p><strong>Free Extension</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Custom sidebar</li>\n<li>Post slider</li>\n<li>Ocean sticks anything</li>\n<li>Demo Import</li>\n<li>Modal Window</li>\n<li>Social sharing</li>\n<li>Product sharing</li>\n<li>Ocean extra</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Premium Extension</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>White Label</li>\n<li>Cookie notice</li>\n<li>Portfolio</li>\n<li>Ocean Hooks</li>\n<li>Sticky Header</li>\n<li>Woo Popup</li>\n<li>Sticky Footer</li>\n<li>Footer Callout</li>\n<li>Side panel</li>\n<li>Instagram</li>\n<li>Popup Login</li>\n<li>Elementor Widgets</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>How to Install OceanWP?</h2>\n<p>For download and installation of the theme, you can go through following easy steps:</p>\n<p><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full\" src=\"http://jeweltheme.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/OcenWP-documentation.png\" alt=\"OcenWP documentation\" width=\"1438\" height=\"824\" /></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Visit the homepage of OceanWP.</li>\n<li>Click on get OceanWP.</li>\n<li>Here you will see the option for download, download the Zip folder of the theme.</li>\n<li>Navigate to the appearance theme.</li>\n<li>Click on Add New button at the top of the page.</li>\n<li>Click on Upload Theme button in the next page.</li>\n<li>Select the file option and choose the ZIP folder of the Theme you have downloaded.</li>\n<li>Click on Install Now option.</li>\n<li>The theme will be installed successfully and finally</li>\n<li>Click on the Activate option. </li>\n</ul>\n<h1>Final Thoughts</h1>\n<p>Finally, we completed with an overall description of OceanWP, an outstanding theme. I hope this article will be helpful for you and you can easily implement it for your upcoming website. OceanWP is really an impressive theme with several elegant features. This is the main reason for its popularity and 400K+ active installs. You can rarely find any free theme with so many amazing features. The best part is, now even a layman can use this theme as it offers well-detailed documentation. Not only that, its amazing customs widgets customize your website in a very attractive way. This theme is one of the best <a href=\"https://www.wpentire.com/free-wordpress-themes/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">free WordPress themes</a> available nowadays.</p>\n<p>If you are searching for a perfect and well-maintained theme for your website then I can assure you, OceanWP is your right choice. You can find a variety of features which is not only amazing but also interesting. You will have a great experience with it.</p>\n<p>If you have any query regarding this theme please comment us in our comment section. We heartily welcome all of those and try to answer it as soon we can. Keep visiting our website for a more interesting theme with amazing features.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</sect